<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>C</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.C            F
 Scumpe Isus, tine-ma
.C          G G7
 langa a Ta cruce,
.C             F
 Caci acolo-i sfant izvor
.C    G  G7   C
 ce salvare-aduce.

[C1]
.  C           F     C    G/B      Em G
   Lauda mea e Isus, ce-a murit pe cruce,
.  C                F      C   G G7  C
   Pana voi ajunge-n cer, la odihna dulce.

[V2]
 Langa cruce am aflat dragostea-Ti divina
 Si a diminetii stea mi-a adus lumina.

[V3]
 Langa cruce voi veghea, stand in asteptare,
 Pana cand voi fi mutat in a Ta splendoare.</lyrics>
<title>Scumpe Isus tine-ma langa a Ta cruce</title>
</song>